---
import Button from '@components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<section class="bg-slate-950 py-20 text-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase text-teal-200">
      Ready for adaptation
    </p>
    <h2 class="mt-4 font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-5xl">
      Keep the architecture. Replace the story.
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-200">
      Genesis is the demo layer. The template structure is built so real
      projects can update content, navigation, and branding without editing
      routing, SEO, or deployment internals.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-3">
      <Button href="/docs">Implementation guide</Button>
      <Button href="/contact" variant="ghost">Test actions</Button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
